name: places/ChIJWxHvMRoQ2jERqdYcd2AsqKI/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUQ2NnBxdUxBEAE
text: {'text': "My new pump that was bought at other shop was suddenly not working in the middle of the night. I was so stressed and look for a 24 hour aquarium shop to get a replacement pump. I called seven star aquarium at past midnight to check if theyre open. Before ending the call, I told the uncle on the phone the condition of my pump. He told me to send a WhatsApp video of my pump. He called me back and gave me a possible solution and told me what may have gone wrong with my pump. He told me to try, then give him call again if it's still not OK. I tried the solution he offered and OMG IT WORKED!! Uncle must be a very knowledgeable and experienced person in this field. I'm so happy. He nvr earn anything from helping me but he helped me anyway. Such a good man. I'm going to his shop soon to get accessories for my new tank and hope to see him and say my thanks. Thank you uncle! You saved my son's new fishes!!", 'languageCode': 'en'}

text: {'text': 'First time buyer of fish and chinese lady boss was quite nice in sharing what to buy and what is needed...etc but prices are high for a neighbourhood shop and lady boss gave some discount\nBought a 2nd batch of fish to add to the tank a week later, was served by the indian lady worker who gave me all five fishes which died within two days....1st good experience ruined by the 2nd visit. Not buying again!', 'languageCode': 'en'}
